sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant App as React Native App
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant DB as Azure SQL

    U->>App: Navigate to Progress tab
    App->>API: GET /exercises/names
    API->>DB: SELECT DISTINCT exercise_name FROM exercise_logs
    DB-->>API: Exercise names
    API-->>App: ["Barbell Bench Press", "Squat", ...]
    App->>U: Show exercise picker

    U->>App: Select "Barbell Bench Press"
    App->>API: GET /exercises/history?name=Barbell+Bench+Press&range=3months
    API->>DB: SELECT weight_kg, reps, logged_at FROM exercise_logs
    DB-->>API: Time-series data
    API-->>App: [{date, weight_kg, reps}, ...]

    App->>App: Render line chart
    App->>App: Render history table
    App->>U: Display progress view
